g green()
r red()

주요 마커¶
o circle()
v triangle_down( )
^ triangle_up()
s square()
+ plus()
. point()
'-' Solid line
':' Dotted line
'--' Dashed line
'-.' Dashed/dotted line

plt.subplots(행, 열) 이용¶

In [60]:
### plot, bar  
x = range(0,15)
y = [v*v for v in x]

fig, axs = plt.subplots(2,2, figsize=(10,10))
axs[0,0].plot(x, y, 'o')
axs[0,1].plot(x, y, '-')
axs[1,0].bar(x, y)
axs[1,1].hist(x, y)

plt.show()

sin, cos 그래프 그려보기¶

In [55]:
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

x = np.arange(0.0, 2 * np.pi, 0.1)
sin_y = np.sin(x)
cos_y = np.cos(x)

plt.figure(figsize=(10,12))
fig, axs = plt.subplots(2)
axs[0].plot(x, sin_y, 'b--')
axs[1].plot(x, cos_y, 'r--')
plt.show()

<Figure size 720x864 with 0 Axes>

(2)

2 2  .
1 1: sin()  
1 2: cos()  ( : )
2 1: tan()  ( : )
2 2: arctan()  ( : )

plt.subplot(3,3,2)

plt.legend(loc='upper center')  # 9

plt.subplot(3,3,3)

plt.legend(loc='upper right')  # 1

plt.plot(x, 1*x, label='y = %ix' % 1)
plt.legend(loc='center left')  # 6

plt.subplot(3,3,5)
plt.plot(x, 1*x, label='y = %ix' % 1)
plt.legend(loc='center')  # 10

plt.legend(loc='center right')  # 5
